eu.excitement.entailment.core

Interface TEDecision


  • public interface TEDecision
    This interface represents the return value for EDA process() results. It only holds the basic information, and EDA implementers are extend to extend it to hold additional information for their EDA.
    Author:
    Gil

    • Method Detail

      • getDecision

        DecisionLabel getDecision()
        this method returns an object of type DecisionLabel as the entailment decision.

      • getConfidence

        double getConfidence()
        this method returns the associated confidence value for the entailment decision. The range is [0,1], and 1 means full confidence. If the value is not meaningful for the EDA, it should return a constant number CONFIDENCE_NOT_AVAILABLE, which is defined in the interface as a constant.

      • getPairID

        java.lang.String getPairID()
        this method returns the entailment.Pair id as described in the CAS.
